{"search_data": "Uttar PradeshUP Yogi Dihadi Majdur Bharan Poshan Bhatta Yojana Online Application Form 2020UP govt. invites Yogi Dihadi Majdur Bharan Poshan Bhatta Yojana online application form at uplabour.gov.in for daily wage workers, labourers apply online or make offline application by downloading registration / application form, daily wage earners to get Rs. 1,000 amid Coronavirus (COVID-19) lockdownTable of Contents  UP Dihadi Majdoor Bharan Poshan Bhatta Yojana 2020Yogi Dihadi Majdur Yojana Online Registration FormUP Pravasi Majdur Bhatta Yojana Offline Application FormUP Majdoor Bhatta Yojana Eligibility Criteria / Documents ListUP Dihadi Majdoor Bharan Poshan Bhatta Yojana 2020The state govt. has started inviting UP Yogi Majdur Bhatta Yojana Application Form 2020 for daily wage labourers. This scheme will ensure that the workers gets adequate assistance from the Uttar Pradesh government.Yogi Dihadi Majdur Yojana Online Registration FormTo assist daily wage labourers, govt. has started various schemes for their welfare and one of the schemes is named as Majdoor Grant Scheme. All the persons who made registration had received Rs. 1,000 in their bank accounts through DBT mode. Below is the complete process to fill UP Yogi Majdur Bhatta online registration form:-Firstly visit the official website at uplabour.gov.inAt the homepage, click at the \u201cOnline Registration and Renewal\u201d tab or directly click this link as shown here:-UP Yogi Majdur Bhatta Yojana Online ApplyThen the UP Labour Act Management System page will open where labourers can make UP Yogi Majdur Bhatta Yojana online registration by clicking \u201cRegister Now\u201d tab as shown below:-UP Yogi Majdur Bhatta Yojana Online RegistrationIn the newly opened page, click at the \u201cNew Registration\u201d tab under \u2018Member Registration\u2019 section. Then you will be redirected to Nivesh Mitra Portal at https://niveshmitra.up.nic.in/.Here fill in all the necessary details and click at the \u201cRegister\u201d button to complete the registration process of labourers.UP Pravasi Majdur Bhatta Yojana Offline Application FormThe daily wage earners can even apply for Yogi Majdur Bhatta Yojana through offline mode, the process is mentioned here:-Daily wage workers are required to go to either municipal council or municipal corporation or civic bodies or gram panchayat for offline avedan.The offline application form for daily wage labourers for Yogi Majdur Bhatta Yojana will appear as shown below:-UP Yogi Majdur Bhatta Yojana Application Form DownloadOnly those labourers whose name is not registered at the UP Labour dept. portal or applicants name is not present in MGNREGA Workers List can only apply.\u092a\u091f\u0930\u0940 \u0926\u0941\u0915\u093e\u0928\u0926\u093e\u0930/ \u0935\u0947\u0902\u0921\u0930, \u0930\u093f\u0915\u094d\u0936\u093e/ \u0924\u093e\u0902\u0917\u093e \u091a\u093e\u0932\u0915, \u091f\u0947\u092e\u094d\u092a\u094b/ \u0911\u091f\u094b/ \u0908 \u0930\u093f\u0915\u094d\u0936\u093e \u091a\u093e\u0932\u0915, \u0926\u0948\u0928\u093f\u0915 \u0926\u093f\u0939\u093e\u095c\u0940 \u092e\u091c\u0926\u0942\u0930/ \u092e\u0902\u0921\u093f\u092f\u094b \u092e\u0947 \u092a\u0932\u094d\u0932\u0947\u0926\u093e\u0930\u0940 \u0915\u0930\u0928\u0947 \u0935\u093e\u0932\u0947 / \u0920\u0947\u0932\u093f\u092f\u093e \u091a\u0932\u093e\u0928\u0947 \u0935\u093e\u0932\u0947, \u0905\u0928\u094d\u092f \u0926\u0948\u0928\u093f\u0915 \u0915\u093e\u0930\u094d\u092f \u0915\u0930\u0928\u0947 \u0935\u093e\u0932\u0947 \u0935\u094d\u092f\u0915\u094d\u0924\u093f can apply offline or online.In municipal council, nominated nodal officer and in municipal corporation or civic bodies, executive officers will make registration of labourers. The collector has been given the responsibility to nominate nodal officer.UP Majdoor Bhatta Yojana Eligibility Criteria / Documents ListIn case you are a daily wage earner, then you must possess some documents for Yogi Majdur Yojana registration to avail scheme benefits:- \u2014 Labourer must be a permanent resident of Uttar Pradesh. \u2014 Labourers must have registration certificate from UP labour department, municipal council / corporation or gram sabha.If the applicant worker is registered in any of the above mentioned departments, then assistance amount would be transferred directly into their bank accounts. Kiln workers can make online registration at the official website www.uplabour.gov.inBenefits of Yogi Majdur Bhatta Yojana \u0907\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0924\u0939\u0924 \u0917\u0930\u0940\u092c \u0926\u093f\u0939\u093e\u0921\u093c\u0940 \u092e\u091c\u0926\u0942\u0930 \u0914\u0930 \u0928\u093f\u0930\u094d\u092e\u093e\u0923 \u0936\u094d\u0930\u092e\u093f\u0915 (\u0930\u093f\u0915\u094d\u0936\u093e \u0935\u093e\u0932\u0947, \u0916\u094b\u092e\u091a\u0947 \u0935\u093e\u0932\u0947, \u0930\u0947\u0939\u0921\u093c\u0940 \u0935\u093e\u0932\u0947, \u092b\u0947\u0930\u0940 \u0935\u093e\u0932\u0947, \u0928\u093f\u0930\u094d\u092e\u093e\u0923 \u0915\u093e\u0930\u094d\u092f \u0915\u0930\u0928\u0947 \u0935\u093e\u0932\u0947) \u0915\u094b \u092f\u0942\u092a\u0940 \u0938\u0930\u0915\u093e\u0930 \u0926\u094d\u0935\u093e\u0930\u093e 1000 \u0930\u0941\u092a\u092f\u0947 \u092e\u0926\u0926 \u0926\u0940 \u091c\u093e \u0930\u0939\u0940 \u0939\u0948.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://www.zeebiz.com/hindi/india/daily-wage-earners-online-registration-money-transfer-get-government-relief-in-lockdown-24669, uplabour.gov.in  at  "}